NAME
    Interchange6::Lexicon::Import - Import locales for Interchange6

VERSION
    0.001

ATTRIBUTES
  lexicon_directory
    The directory where we store the *.pod files.

  locales
    Hash reference with locales. The hash values are
    Interchange6::Lexicon::Locale objects.

  po_encoding
    Encoding of the *.po files, defaults to `UTF-8'.

  read_locales
    Read locales from "lexicon_directory".

  write_locales
    Write locales into "lexicon_directory.

